name: Chocolate Chip Cookie
description: Our delicious buttery cookie with generous chunks of dark and milk chocolates.

name: Peanut Butter Cookie
description: Sweet Rich, and Gluten Free! this cookie is about as close as you can get to eating peanut butter straight out of the jar with a spoon.

name: Snickerdoodle
description: A New England classic! Try our buttery sugar cookie with cinnamon and a cinnamon crackle shell.

name: Oatmeal Raisin Cookie
description: Possibly the most controversial cookie ever, but sure to please your Grandma, our oatmeal raisin cookie is soft and loaded with golden raisins.

name: Corn Cookie
description: Yup, you read that right. It's like delicious sweet cornbread but in cookie form.

name: Sugar Cookie
description: Sometimes the classics are the best. Sweet, buttery, and with just a hint of Vanilla.

name: Vanilla/Vanilla Cupcake
description: The base by which all cupcakes are measured. Fluffy vanilla cake topped with buttery vanilla icing.

name: Vanilla/Chocolate Cupcake
description: Our famous vanilla cake with rich chocolate icing made with 75% cacao dark chocoalte.

name: Death by Chocolate Cupcake
description: Chocolate cake, filled with fudge, with chocolate icing, and chocolate crunch nonpareils on top. If you don't die, you'll definitely come back for more.

name: Lemon Raspberry Cupcake
description: Vanilla cake filled to bursting with raspberry compote, topped with a tart whipped lemon chiffon icing.

name: Oreo Cupcake
description: Chocolate cake with a vanilla cream center, topped with vanilla icing and crushed cookie bits. It's like a real oreo on top of a backwards oreo. Either way it's delicious!

name: Black Forest Cake
description: The classic mix of chocolate and cherry, guaranteed to be a crowd pleaser. Buy two and hide one from your family!

name: Celebration Cake
description: Your choice of cake base and frosting flavor, built into an exquisite cake with a custom message.

name: Carrot Cake
description: Guaranteed to make rabbits wild, we use 4 whole carrots in each cake, and add our signature blend of spices to make it magical. And of course, cream cheese icing.

name: Red Velvet Cake
description: Blah blah blah, you're just here for the cream cheese icing, and that's ok.

name: Chocolate Lava Cake
description: Rich chocolate cake with a molten core of dark fudge.

name: Brownie
description: Our brownies are rich with a nice chew and crackly top. No cake by another name here!

name: Raspberry Crunch Bar
description: Cinnamon shortbread topped with a layer of raspberry jam and almond streussel, baked golden brown.

name: Lemon Squares
description: Tart and sweet!

name: Key Lime Bars
description: Like a Lemon Square, but with key limes. Oh, and a toasted coconut topping!

name: Croissant
description: The Parisian classic made from scratch with whole butter.

name: Chocolate Croissant
description: Flaky croissant enveloping dark chocolate batons.

name: Cheese Danish
description: Flaky pastry with a sweet cream cheese center.

name: Blueberry Scone
description: Our crumbly, melt-in-your-mouth scone is perfectly balanced with sweet blueberries and lemon icing.

name: Plain Bagel
description: Chewy on the outside, soft on the inside, the closet you can get to NYC without crossing a bridge.

name: Cinnnamon Raisin Bagel
description: Our (some would say) perfect bagel, kissed with cinnamon and smattered with raisins throughout. Just sweet enough for your tooth.

name: Everything Bagel
description: Let our everything be your everything in the morning.

name: Quiche Lorraine
description: What could be better than a slice of baconny, cheesy, onion-y quiche in the morning..? Can't think of anything.

name: Broccoli Cheddar Quiche
description: Go ahead, tell me veggies aren't delicious. They are when surrounded by smoke cheddar cheese and savory custard.

name: Market Veggie Quiche
description: Loaded with the freshest of the fresh veggies from the farmers' market, this quiche will get you off on the right foot.
